// Orchicon Policy entity (docs/02_Domain_Model.md §2.5, docs/07 §3.5).
//
// Policy is a first-class, versioned, reusable rule evaluated by the
// Policy Engine at well-defined decision points. Tier 1 (decision-point)
// policy is the v0.1 baseline, always-on, Rego-only (Open Policy Agent).
// Tier 2 (per-tool-call gating) is opt-in per Worker and surfaces through
// ExecutionService.ApproveToolCall; Go hooks are deferred to v0.2.
